OL,3,CWelsh Government to set out 'targeted
OL,4,Cchange' to 20mph
OL,6,FSome Welsh roads could to revert to a
OL,7,F30mph speed limit by the end of the
OL,8,Fyear after new guidance and funding
OL,9,Fwas announced today.
OL,11,FTransport Secretary Ken Skates has
OL,12,Finsisted this is not a change in
OL,13,Fpolicy, or in the legislation, but
OL,14,Finstead "new guidance" around the
OL,15,Freduction in speed limits.
