OL,3,CWelsh Government to set out 'targeted
OL,4,Cchange' to 20mph
OL,6,FMr Skates has pledged to set out a
OL,7,Fthree-phase plan on 20mph, where the
OL,8,FWelsh Government will work with local
OL,9,Fauthorities to revise the guidance on
OL,10,Fwhich local roads can be exempted from
OL,11,F20mph.
OL,13,FThe revised guidance will be published
OL,14,Fin July, with councils expected to
OL,15,Fmake changes from September.
