OL,3,CWelsh Government to set out 'targeted
OL,4,Cchange' to 20mph
OL,6,FSince September 2023, local
OL,7,Fauthorities in Wales have been obliged
OL,8,Fto set speed limits in urban and
OL,9,Fresidential areas at 20mph as a
OL,10,Fdefault, becoming the first UK nation
OL,11,Fto do so.
OL,13,FThe policy has been controversial
OL,14,Fsince it came into force, with nearly
OL,15,F470,000 signatures on a petition to
OL,16,Frevert the lowering of the speed limit.
OL,18,FCouncils have already been allowed to
OL,19,Fmake some exemptions to keep certain
OL,20,Froads at 30mph.
