OL,3,CWelsh Government to set out 'targeted
OL,4,Cchange' to 20mph
OL,6,FBut today in the Senedd, Ken Skates
OL,7,Ftold fellow politicians there will be
OL,8,Fa "national listening programme"
OL,9,Fputting the "voice of Welsh citizens"
OL,10,Fat the heart of deciding which roads
OL,11,Fcan return to 30mph.
OL,13,FSpeaking to ITV Cymru Wales, Mr Skates
OL,14,Fsaid: "It's not a u-turn. We are
OL,15,Frefining the policy and making sure
OL,16,Fthat we acknowledge that the vast
OL,17,Fmajority of people in Wales believe
OL,18,Fthat slower speeds are ideal outside
OL,19,Fhospitals, schools, nurseries and busy
OL,20,Fand built-up residential areas."
