OL,3,CWelsh Government to set out 'targeted
OL,4,Cchange' to 20mph
OL,6,FHe continued: "We accept that some
OL,7,Froads should be 30mph whereas at the
OL,8,Fmoment they are 20mph. We want to help
OL,9,Fcouncils make the change back and that
OL,10,Fmeans looking at the guidance.
OL,12,F"Crucially it means listening to
OL,13,Fpeople, getting public opinion, taking
OL,14,Faccount of the heat this debate has
OL,15,Fgenerated and hopefully, by the end of
OL,16,Fthe process, bring people together in
OL,17,Fa place where 20mph is a popular
OL,18,Fpolicy in those areas where it's most
OL,19,Fsuitable."
