OL,6,FHe added: "If there are routes that
OL,7,Fshould revert back to 30mph, we will
OL,8,Fmove swiftly to ensure that happens."
OL,10,FResponding to the announcement, the
OL,11,FShadow Minister for Transport and
OL,12,FTechnology said very little about the
OL,13,Fpolicy had changed.
