OL,4,Cchange' to 20mph
OL,6,FNatasha Asghar said: "I think for the
OL,7,Flast week he has been saying all the
OL,8,Fright things and hitting the right
OL,9,Fnote for the public, I've had an
OL,10,Finflux of messages, emails and calls
OL,11,Ffrom residents all across Wales saying
OL,12,F'Oh the minister is rescinding and
OL,13,FLabour's going back on his word' -
OL,14,Fthat's not the case.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/10
