OL,3,CWelsh Government to set out 'targeted
OL,4,Cchange' to 20mph
OL,6,F"Until the minister actually stands on
OL,7,Fthe chamber and says 'I am rescinding,
OL,8,Fthe 20mph blanket speed that exists
OL,9,Fcurrently back to 30mph' as per the
OL,10,Fpetition. That's what people of Wales
OL,11,Fhave wanted and asked for... Until he
OL,12,Fsays, 'yes Natasha, that's what going
OL,13,Fto happen' it's just words."
OL,15,FReacting to the news that some roads
OL,16,Fcould return to 30mph, one woman said:
OL,17,F"Brilliant. It takes me ages to come
OL,18,Fhere to work. It depends on the roads
OL,19,F- I always take care. It's just common
OL,20,Fsense, really."
