OL,3,CWelsh Government to set out 'targeted
OL,4,Cchange' to 20mph
OL,6,F"I think it's been very difficult
OL,7,Fdriving at 20 - hardly anyone ever
OL,8,Fdoes it. I can understand schools and
OL,9,Fhospitals, but otherwise it's been
OL,10,Fcrazy. I think they've made a big
OL,11,Fmistake," one man, in favour of the
OL,12,Fnew guidance, said.
OL,14,F"I'm not for people exceeding the
OL,15,Fspeed limit and I'm all for people
OL,16,Fbeing safe, but I think bringing it
OL,17,Fdown to 20mph is maybe a bit too far,"
OL,18,Fanother woman said.
